e9665b2ba1c3445bc927fc9","tid":1369423,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:00:28.000Z","msg":"你既意思係 冇大台 每個人都可以發聲 不論勇武定和理非 不論黃藍 自己作主 <br />\n咁係咪應該尊重每個人既意見 而唔係推到某個人仆街？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:49:43.000Z","msg":"岩 無錯<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割席，不譴責，不阻止</span></span></strong><br />\n但前題係細良都要尊重勇武，你能夠好言相勸，但如果勇武要做既話，唔可以阻止對方，唔可以話對方係鬼，出左咩事就一齊互相cover，學習，努力做文宣，我地從6/9 ，6/12走機，始終如一<br />\n<br />\n因為要堅持呢幾個信念先能夠行到呢步，政府終將出黑社會<br />\n和理非<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化，不割席，不譴責，不阻止</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n勇武<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不受傷，不流血，不被捕</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"983fc50a0db7b376cf362c6db05dbd9a10948af3","tid":1369423,"uid":42981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:53:31.000Z","msg":"標題撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2369e3b8a745c9b13e029abf61e4b7a0ecd19b","tid":1369423,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:55:04.000Z","msg":"fact check?"},{"pid":"b6504d3e5a072540065a31ce5cafc81b11e85644","tid":1369423,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:59:06.000Z","msg":"明顯三毛啦，標題嚇人但內容完全係呀媽係女人嘅廢話。"},{"pid":"8d817a5910b3a8e362d034e567195c249ec1419a","tid":1369423,"uid":122059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b85c65c25029a04588ca7e64fef6d1c5973c855e","tid":1369423,"uid":231905,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:55:59.000Z","msg":"唔撚識寫標題，對唔住咁多位，但內容真係希望大家睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:59:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 標題黨<br />\n如果你有細心聽佢分析 再用下自己個腦思考<br />\n可以話係合理既推論<br />\n如果佢唔合理 你隨時反駁佢<br />\n無撚係度造謠生事 